code: function ChangeSinceLoad(initialBikeCount,currentBikeCount,timeSinceUpdate){var minutesAgo=parseInt(timeSinceUpdate/60000);var timeAgo="0 minutes ago";if(minutesAgo===0){timeAgo="just now.";}else if(minutesAgo===1){timeAgo="1 minute ago.";}else{timeAgo=minutesAgo.toString()+" minutes ago.";}var bikeChange=currentBikeCount-initialBikeCount;if(bikeChange===0){return"Number of bikes is same as when station status was first loaded "+timeAgo;}else if(bikeChange>1){return bikeChange.toString()+" more bikes since station status was first was loaded "+timeAgo;}else if(bikeChange===1){return"1 more bike since station status was first was loaded "+timeAgo;}else if(bikeChange<-1){return(-bikeChange).toString()+" fewer bikes since station status was first was loaded "+timeAgo;}else if(bikeChange===-1){return"1 fewer bike since station status was first was loaded "+timeAgo;}}export default ChangeSinceLoad;
